data.text:
SA Premix was founded in 2002 in the picturesque town, Burgersdorp, Eastern Cape. Our first delivery was to a client in the Western Cape on 11 November 2004.

In 2020 we rebranded as AECI Animal Health and are part of the AECI Agri Health Pillar.

AECI Animal Health is a key role player in the South African animal feed industry. We specialise in manufacturing animal feed premixes of the highest quality for all species.

Our core competencies

Manufacture high quality animal feed premixes to customer specifications

Import and supply feed grade commodities

Represent and distribute local and international products in the animal health, nutraceutical and specialised veterinary markets.

We have certification for AFMA, FAMI Q and ISO 9001:2015 and comply with requisite European Standards.

Through our international partners we provide technical information on a wide range of topics across all species.
